title: UEFA Europa League all-time top goalscorers 1971 to 2019
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Goals scored for 23 number of Months.

The highest Month Henrik Larsson has 18.0 more Goals scored than the lowest Month Jürgen Klinsmann.
